These are Puzzles for 3x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-1::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: classical, house, pop
There are 3 different nationalities: indian, thai, turkish
There are 3 different favourite colors: blue, lavender, ivory
1. the person who likes ivory is in an even position##4
2. the thai is on the left of the indian##1
3. the fan of classical is on the right of the person who likes blue##1
4. the thai is in an even position##4
5. the fan of pop is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |    3     |
| Music-Genre   | pop       | classical     | house    |
| Nationality   | turkish   | thai          | indian   |
| Color         | blue | ivory | lavender |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-2::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: adventure, scientific, thriller
The people have 3 different hobbies: chess, collecting, video-games
The people have 3 different jobs:  dancer, musician, teacher
1. the teacher is the person watching thriller movies##1
2. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left or right of the teacher##3
3. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
4. the musician is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
5. the teacher is in an even position##4
6. the teacher is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |    3     |
| Movie-Genre    | adventure     | thriller  | scientific  |
| Hobby   | video-games | collecting | chess    |
| Job     | dancer      | teacher    | musician |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-3::.
There 3 different types of food: apple, kiwi, plum
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: funk, hip-hop, reggae
There are 3 different nationalities: turkish, egyptian, italian
1. the turkish is in an even position##4
2. the italian is the person eating apple##1
3. the fan of reggae is on the right of the fan of funk##1
4. the person eating plum is on the right of the person eating apple##1
5. the person eating plum is on the left or right of the fan of reggae##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |   3    |
| Food          | apple         | plum     | kiwi   |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop       | funk     | reggae |
| Nationality         | italian | turkish | egyptian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-4::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: coffee, hot-chocolate, mirinda
The people have 3 different jobs:  social-worker, teacher, writer
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, dannemann, bolivar
1. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the bolivar-smoker##1
2. the dannemann-smoker is on the right of the writer##1
3. the social-worker is in an odd position##4
4. the person drinking coffee is on the far left##1
5. the writer is on the far left or far right##3
6. the teacher is on the right of the writer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2     |       3       |
| Beverage   | coffee | mirinda  | hot-chocolate |
| Job        | writer | teacher  | social-worker |
| Cigar        | swisher | dannemann | bolivar         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-5::.
There 3 different types of food: grapefruit, lettuce, zucchini
There are 3 different nationalities: american, australian, chinese
3 different pets are kept: bird, chinchilla, mouse
1. the american is on the left or right of the owner of the bird##3
2. the australian is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
3. the owner of the bird is on the right of the person eating grapefruit##1
4. the owner of the bird is in an odd position##4
5. the person eating zucchini is on the far left##1
6. the person eating lettuce is on the left or right of the person eating grapefruit##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |
| Food   | zucchini | grapefruit  | lettuce  |
| Nationality   | australian  | american | chinese |
| Pet           | chinchilla  | mouse    | bird    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-6::.
3 different pets are kept: mouse, cat, rabbit
The people have 3 different hobbies: board-games, chess, singing
The people use 3 different means of transport: boat, car, quad-bike
1. the owner of the mouse is between the person driving the quad-bike and the person who's hobby is singing##2
2. the person who's hobby is board-games is the owner of the cat##1
3. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
4. the person driving the car is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |   2   |      3      |
| Pet    | rabbit  | mouse  | cat        |
| Hobby       | singing | chess | board-games |
| Transport   | boat    | car   | quad-bike   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-7::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: pop, folk, electronic
3 different pets are kept: frog, goldfish, rat
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: golf, skateboarding, tennis
1. the fan of folk is between the owner of the frog and the fan of electronic##2
2. the owner of the rat is on the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
3. the person who's sport is skateboarding is in an even position##4
4. the fan of folk is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |       2       |    3    |
| Music-Genre   | pop | folk        | electronic |
| Pet           | frog   | goldfish      | rat     |
| Sport         | tennis | skateboarding | golf    |

