.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-10::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  chef, nurse, photographer
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: epic, martial-arts, time-travel
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: june, january, december
1. the nurse is on the far right##1
2. the person watching martial-arts movies is the person watching martial-arts movies##1
3. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in december##3
4. the chef is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
5. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
6. the person watching time-travel movies is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |    3    |
| Job           | photographer | chef        | nurse   |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts | time-travel | epic    |
| Birthday   | december         | june      | january |

