1. the person who's sport is water-polo is the person who's sport is water-polo##1
2. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left or right of the person who's sport is water-polo##3
3. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
4. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the musician##1
5. the electrician is on the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
6. the person who's hobby is hiking is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3     |
| Hobby         | cooking   | camping     | hiking   |
| Job           | mechanic  | electrician | musician |
| Sport   | water-polo | baseball     | biathlon |

