.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-17::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  paramedic, pilot, social-worker
3 different pets are kept: bird, chinchilla, rat
3 different games are played: snooker, canasta, scrabble
1. the person playing scrabble is on the far left##1
2. the paramedic is in an even position##4
3. the social-worker is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
4. the pilot is the owner of the chinchilla##1
5. the owner of the rat is on the right of the owner of the bird##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2     |       3       |
| Job     | pilot      | paramedic | social-worker |
| Pet     | chinchilla | bird      | rat           |
| Game   | scrabble | snooker  | canasta    |

