.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-18::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: mirinda, sprite, tea
City: edinburgh, venice, san-francisco
The people use 3 different means of transport: helicopter, jet-ski, train
1. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
2. the person driving the helicopter is on the left or right of the person driving the train##3
3. the person traveling to san-francisco is in an odd position##4
4. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
5. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
6. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left or right of the person driving the helicopter##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |     3      |
| Beverage    | mirinda | tea      | sprite     |
| City         | venice  | edinburgh | san-francisco        |
| Transport   | jet-ski | train    | helicopter |

